snippet.title: Mario Party: The Top 100 - Game Modes & amiibo Trailer - Nintendo 3DS
snippet.description:
Test your memory, speed, and luck in a variety of game modes in Mario Party: The Top 100. You can also check out how amiibo figures bring more fun to the party! 

Mario Party: The Top 100 is available November 10th! https://goo.gl/TGUpr5
